Introduction

Chaness was a subunit of LPG, formed under Aquargo Entertainment/Chan2 Productions. Their lineup consisted of Lahee, Jiwon, Riwon, Songha, and Jieun. They debuted on August 20, 2014 with their single, “SeSeSe”. In 2016, the unit ended as a result of LPG disbanding.
